# EEE4113F_Group12_PCB
## Overview
This repository was used for Group 12 (of the 2026 EEE4113F course from the University of Cape Town) to collaborate on the design of the B.A.R.B.I.E.

Buoy for<br>
Antarctic<br>
Research and<br>
Basic<br>
Information<br>
Exchange

HTML file contains the UI for the B.A.R.B.I.E called T.E.A.
KiCAD files contains the pcb designs
embedded_software contains the various functions used to communicate using LoRa and WiFi, receive GPS locations, and manage data processing
